{"tid":2458392,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私家診所指科興「聲譽不好」　衞生署回收疫苗","createTime":"2021-03-23T11:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T01:50:57.000Z","uid":30788,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c6cbf4d30fb8f310fd8abcaaeaea2162c2df7fd1","tid":2458392,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:31:43.000Z","msg":"Now新聞台】衞生署指一間私家診所違反新冠疫苗接種計劃條款協議，即時回收診所的科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n涉事診所為土瓜灣仁澤醫務中心的劉東華醫生診所，網上早前流傳照片顯示，診所貼出資料指科興生產商「聲譽不好」及建議「不打」。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署表示，向相關診所以電話聯絡及上門調查，根據調查所得，涉事醫生違反新冠疫苗接種計劃下私家診所條款協議，已於周一終止與該診所的協議，並即時回收尚未使用的科興疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署提醒私家醫生提供接種服務時，必須嚴格按照衞生署指引。"},{"pid":"cf1db7f551a98e68bcd9f4cc64b25c9ef2ed211c","tid":2458392,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:33:28.000Z","msg":"邊個醫管局膠層打科興?證明「聲譽不好」係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc10bb6f0a926623717e8224b5cbcf8881f2edc","tid":2458392,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:34:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20200814/s00010/3cd708fd04fa4af5b0fbec16af5b8e79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20200814%2Fs00010%2F3cd708fd04fa4af5b0fbec16af5b8e79.jpg&h=0c86ea0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/117730849_3325343927509130_5773022587264366380_o.png?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=1-3&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=68_vbsrY3VwAX-77-D5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg6-1.fna&amp;oh=6ee1e12548f6fe296f936a2a9071e376&amp;oe=60807CE7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg6-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F117730849_3325343927509130_5773022587264366380_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26ccb%3D1-3%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3D68_vbsrY3VwAX-77-D5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg6-1.fna%26oh%3D6ee1e12548f6fe296f936a2a9071e376%26oe%3D60807CE7&h=35d00f0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.n